query:
WITH Ranked AS (
                SELECT
                    Message_Root_Hash,
                    Chain_Id,
                    Block_Number,
                    ROW_NUMBER()
                        OVER (PARTITION BY Chain_Id ORDER BY Block_Number DESC)
                    AS Rn
                FROM Message_Roots
            )
            
            SELECT Message_Root_Hash, Chain_Id, Block_Number
            FROM Ranked
            WHERE Rn <= 5
            ORDER BY Chain_Id, Block_Number DESC;
